rows.label: bf10100100_0010
rows.name:
This used to be a city it seems.
A very ancient one at that.

rows.label: bf10100100_0020
rows.name: This reminds me exactly of the Land of Mors.

rows.label: bf10100100_0030
rows.name:
Probably because it's so dry here.
It's even dustier than that place.

rows.label: bf10100100_0050
rows.name: Looks like it was a child's toy vehicle.

rows.label: bf10100100_0080
rows.name: It must have been a massive city.

rows.label: bf10100100_0090
rows.name: I can't even tell how far it stretches.

rows.label: bf10100100_0100
rows.name:
This city probably held more people
than the entire population of Alst...
